MARCSubfieldLabel: Universal Decimal Classification number (NR), Common auxiliary subdivision (R)
Transformation Notes:
<work> rdawo:P10256 <ConceptUDC(value of $a)> . // Concept for full edition and normalized $a
<ConceptUDC(value of $a)> skos:notation “value of $a”^^<SchemeNotationUDC> . // normalized $a
<ConceptUDC(value of $a)> skos:altLabel “value of $a” . // normalized $a
<ConceptUDC(value of $a)> skos:inScheme http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/classSchemes/“udc”. // tScheme(schemeCode) for 080 ind1=0 = http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/classSchemes/ + “udc” + “Full” + $2
